<tr valign="middle">
<td style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Earth_flag_PD.jpg" class="image"><img alt="Portal icon" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f3/Earth_flag_PD.jpg/32px-Earth_flag_PD.jpg" width="32" height="21" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f3/Earth_flag_PD.jpg/48px-Earth_flag_PD.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f3/Earth_flag_PD.jpg/64px-Earth_flag_PD.jpg 2x" /></a></td>
